ich left her unable to dress herself.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 711, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999998249223, \"rank\": 1.6826222138439254e-10, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Theboxer\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"the welterweight division\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"-66kg)atParis 2024having\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"a Covid-inflicted attack\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"her nervous system\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has since caught Covid on three further occasions but insists she isready to take on the world in the ringhaving booked her place with bronze at last year's European Games.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\", \"score\": 0.9796399721654895, \"rank\": 0.01973787201962562, \"text\": \"European Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"three further occasions\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"the ringhaving\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"her place\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eccles' selection has now been officially ratified by the British Olympic Association (BOA) and if the Welsh fighter makes it to the medal rounds, she will compete at the iconic home of French tennis.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999998075977786, \"rank\": 1.9240214182959512e-07, \"text\": \"BOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7842916349360193, \"rank\": 0.1617441314215797, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eccles' selection\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"the Welsh fighter\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal rounds\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"the iconic home\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether Murray will also do so remains unconfirmed but Eccles has taken heart from the story of the two-time Olympic champion as she prepares for her own big stage bow.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1268, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 0.9999999065935342, \"rank\": 9.340245424948454e-08, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"score\": 0.9999997913773986, \"rank\": 2.0691318801588082e-07, \"text\": \"Eccles\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heart\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"the two-time Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"her own big stage bow\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not someone who has many role models but he is definitely one,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"many role models\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His grit and determination is really inspiring.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His grit\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love the way he plays and chases the ball down, I can be a bit like a dog with a bone sometimes so I can relate to that.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"a dog\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"a bone\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always looked up to his mentality.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his mentality\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think a lot about how strong he is to have come back from what he has been through.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always had setbacks myself.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"setbacks\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got turned away from boxing gyms as a kid, I have had serious injuries, but I have built so much resilience.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boxing gyms\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"serious injuries\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"so much resilience\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I truly believe I can deal with anything.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be ready to go come the Olympics and I have that inner confidence I can make it happen when it matters.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"that inner confidence\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited, there is a lot of pressure on it and it's so hard to get gold.\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I know if I turn up and bring my best, I can do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Known as 'right arm Rosie', Eccles missed out on Tokyo qualification before her Covid nightmare and had to watch on from the other side of the world as long-time sparring partner Lauren Price soared to the top of the podium.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2268, \"end\": 2273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McCall's\", \"score\": 0.71088284991465, \"rank\": 0.40536888312359814, \"text\": \"Rosie\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wiki