 \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"both hands\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this is my Olympics and it's up to me to go and do the same.\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my Olympics\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It means so much more having missed out last time.\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know people say this a lot but I think certain things are just meant to be.\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"certain things\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time, it felt so unfair - and I am not normally someone who says things like that.\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3602}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3653}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it reinforced how much it meant to me.\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have put my body through three years of hell in pursuit of this goal and it will all be worth it if I bring home gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3742}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3762}, {\"ngram\": \"hell\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3770}, {\"ngram\": \"pursuit\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3781}, {\"ngram\": \"this goal\", \"from\": 3785, \"to\": 3794}, {\"ngram\": \"home gold\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The proud Welshwoman who 'always fights with the dragon on my chest' is set to benefit from Aldi's Nearest & Dearest programme in Paris.\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3939, \"end\